precis:
Amendments to the MOTOR VEHICLE SAFETY REGULATIONS which make provision for
the interprovincial shipment of a motor vehicle that does not have the
national safety mark affixed to it where the vehicle is shipped for the
purposes of exhibition, demonstration, evaluation or testing.
